title: MNF Recap Packers-Vikings; Beastmode returns
itunes:title: MNF Recap Packers-Vikings; Beastmode returns
description:
A garage filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal, and Keith Hanzus recap the showdown between the Packers and the Vikings.(4:20 The heroes then bring you all of the latest news surrounding the NFL including Mike McCarthy interviewing with the Panthers (20:33) and the return of Beastmode to Seattle! (24:45)
